{"tid":1426211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"千祈！唔好汁催淚彈頭去機場做展覽！！！","createTime":"2019-08-07T01:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T03:01:18.000Z","uid":72700,"like":97,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7741262c0d714b66f7f0961cc1f0abb450796db2","tid":1426211,"uid":72700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:21:05.000Z","msg":"有friend話見到連登有人提議汁催淚彈頭去機場做展覽，千祈唔好咁做啊！！<br />\n<br />\n根據《火器及彈藥條例》，彈藥包括任何炮彈殼或槍彈殼，任何人將之搬運至另一地方都須先申領牌照，否則可被判囚3個月及罰款5000元；如涉無牌管有彈藥，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最高刑罰可被判囚14年</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />及罰款10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n唔好比黑警有原因拉人而白白送頭啊！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議大家用相算啦！！！"},{"pid":"a04e82199c3fcdb404d9b452d8af3e15f44ab2d6","tid":1426211,"uid":72700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:23:14.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"b3311d00e0c52ebbb07ae4ddf0f23cbcdc022aa0","tid":1426211,"uid":72700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:25:12.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"73f4027afd2007456b6d21c3971a1d3d929cfc30","tid":1426211,"uid":72700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:28:00.000Z","msg":"PUSH!"},{"pid":"d0d0aef80bcb2ea9970cb28d69ef07a7d973fcf6","tid":1426211,"uid":236442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:29:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6adfbf99d20fd926fe8b4d4e2f68409499f09cc5","tid":1426211,"uid":72700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:29:08.000Z","msg":"點解要負皮?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2ef71ec6941a33a855e961f36ce72dd581c190","tid":1426211,"uid":5405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0